    "Furthermore, in their work [67] the authors introduced an optimized and comprehensive framework for resource management within a Blockchain-enabled software-defined Internet of Things (IoTs) ecosystem.",
    "The framework incorporates a novel cluster-head selection algorithm and a distributed flow-rule verification technique, ensuring network consistency and security.",
